      "bullets": [
        "Attackers exploited Meta’s AI support systems to bypass verification, enabling unauthorized takeovers of high-value Instagram accounts.",
        "The incident exposes the severe risk of delegating sensitive account recovery and authentication workflows to automated AI support chatbots.",
        "Organizations must enforce human-in-the-loop verification and strict guardrails to prevent adversarial manipulation of customer-facing AI agents."
      ]
